originalText.text: I highly recommend Aspire Down Under! My husband and I were lucky enough to work with Joanne, who planned our three week long honeymoon to both New Zealand and Australia. Joanne made everything so easy. She was communicative, answered all of our questions and perfectly tailored our excursions and accommodations to our preferences. It was the trip of a lifetime thanks to Aspire Down Under. Thanks again Joanne!

originalText.text: We worked with Sarah W to plan our trip to New Zealand, Australia and Bali.  She listened to our desires as to what to do, type of hotels, tours, etc., we like, what we for sure wanted to see and the trip did not disappoint!  It was a trip of a lifetime, 26 days and everything, and I mean everything went perfectly, without a hitch!  The drivers, tours, were all on time, the hotels were all perfect, like I said, everything went perfectly, very smoothly!  I would recommend Aspire Down Under as well as Sarah.  She was friendly, attentive, responsive, knowledgeable, I cannot say enough about her.  If you are planning a trip down under, do not hesitate to call her!

originalText.text:
My wife and I were privileged to have worked with Sarah W. of Aspire Down Under for a month-long journey through Australia and New Zealand. We were so lucky to find her as she planned the most magnificent time for us. Over the course of many conversations, she patiently listened to our objectives and concerns, and developed an itinerary that could not be beat.

While on the trip, we kept marveling how there was nothing we would change and how brilliant Sarah was in fitting together all the pieces of a complex puzzle.

We unequivocally recommend her for a travel advisor to this part of the world and have every confidence that she will do a tremendous job.

Thank you again for the amazing trip!

originalText.text: Sarah put together a true bucket list trip! Starting with the beautiful Denarau Island, Fiji, before hitting Sydney, Port Douglas, Great Barrier Reef, Melbourne and the Great Ocean Road. We saw wild Koala’s, Kangaroos, Wallabees, Cockatoos and Turtles. Truly amazing!
